WEBVTT

00:07.341 --> 00:08.718
Can you give us an
account of your whereabouts

00:08.884 --> 00:11.353
throughout Friday
and into Friday evening?

00:11.512 --> 00:13.685
I was with my brother Ciaran,
in his shop.

00:13.847 --> 00:15.520
Move it, move it!

00:15.682 --> 00:16.433
Move it, go!

00:16.600 --> 00:18.273
Hildur's glacier hotel.

00:18.435 --> 00:20.904
She can't go ahead
without government say-so.

00:21.063 --> 00:23.157
Charlie said in his message

00:23.315 --> 00:25.363
that he'd found something
that changed everything.

00:25.526 --> 00:26.743
<i>Deleted.</i>

00:26.902 --> 00:29.280
Do you think
it's a mammoth's tooth?

00:29.446 --> 00:31.744
Well, if it turns
out that's what it is...

00:31.907 --> 00:33.375
Please call me.

00:33.534 --> 00:34.751
And only me.

00:34.910 --> 00:36.878
Is this what got him killed?

00:37.037 --> 00:38.289
What have you done?

00:38.455 --> 00:39.752
Where did you go?

00:39.915 --> 00:41.212
Are you seeing anybody?

00:41.375 --> 00:42.797
ls that an official question?

00:46.922 --> 00:51.769
♪ The river did come to me ♪

00:51.927 --> 00:57.149
♪ Straight into my arms ♪

00:57.307 --> 01:01.107
♪ I tried to caress it ♪

01:01.270 --> 01:05.571
♪ But it ran
through my fingertips... ♪

01:08.318 --> 01:12.824
♪ Water will keep running,
rivers will turn ♪

01:12.990 --> 01:17.587
♪ Water will keep running
and rivers will turn ♪

01:17.744 --> 01:22.124
♪ Water will keep running,
rivers will turn ♪

01:22.291 --> 01:28.139
♪ Water will keep running
and rivers will turn. ♪

